    "description": "The CN6000 Series is a high-speed hardware encryption platform designed to secure data transmitted over Ethernet and Fibre Channel networks. The CN6040 is protocol selectable operating at line rates up to 4Gb/s. Configured in Ethernet mode the CN6040 supports optical and twisted-pair link rates of 10Mb/s, 100Mb/s & 1Gb/s whilst in Fibre Channel mode supports rates of 1.0625, 2.125 & 4.25Gb/s. The CN6100 is an Ethernet model that operates at a line rate of 10Gb/s. SafeNet, Inc. makes Senetas products available globally under a master distribution agreement and are co-branded as such.",
